4x^2 + 4x + 5 = 4\left(x^2 + x + \frac{5}{4}\right).
4x^2 + 4x + 5 = 4\left(x+\frac{1}{2}\right)^2 + \mathrm{const}
4x^2 + 4x + 5 = 4\left(x + \frac{1}{2} \right)^2 + 4 = (2x + 1)^2 + 4
